### Erase / Remove packages
#### Using rpm -e
NOTE: Problem with this is will not remove dependancies!!!
```
$ rpm -qa |grep -i bind-utils
bind-utils-9.16.23-15.el9.x86_64
$ rpm -e bind-utils-9.16.23-15.el9.x86_64         <-- this will remove th pkg
$ rpm -qa |grep -i bind-utils
$
```


#### Using yum
```
